sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist<br/>(Browser)
    participant Dashboard as RHOAI Dashboard<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant K8sAPI as OpenShift API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant NotebookCtrl as ODH Notebook<br/>Controller
    participant Kubelet as OpenShift Kubelet
    participant Quay as quay.io/modh<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Workbench as Workbench Pod<br/>8888/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,Workbench: Flow 1: Workbench Image Selection and Launch

    User->>Dashboard: Select workbench type<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: OAuth2 / OIDC
    Dashboard->>K8sAPI: Read ImageStream tags<br/>HTTPS/6443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Dashboard: ImageStream metadata<br/>(annotations, image refs)
    Dashboard->>K8sAPI: Create Notebook CR<br/>HTTPS/6443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token

    NotebookCtrl->>K8sAPI: Watch Notebook CR
    K8sAPI-->>NotebookCtrl: Notebook CR event
    NotebookCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create StatefulSet<br/>+ Service + HTTPRoute<br/>HTTPS/6443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    Kubelet->>Quay: Pull workbench image<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Pull secret (SHA256 digest)
    Quay-->>Kubelet: Container image layers

    Note over User,Workbench: User accesses workbench

    User->>Workbench: Access workbench UI<br/>HTTPS/443 → HTTP/8888<br/>TLS terminated at ingress<br/>Auth: kube-rbac-proxy sidecar

    Workbench-->>User: JupyterLab / RStudio / VS Code UI

    Note over User,Workbench: Flow 2: Konflux Image Build (PR)

    participant Dev as Developer
    participant GitHub as GitHub PR<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant PaC as Pipelines-as-Code
    participant Tekton as Tekton PipelineRun
    participant Registry as Container Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Dev->>GitHub: Push PR<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: GitHub token
    PaC->>Tekton: Trigger PipelineRun<br/>CEL filter on changed paths
    Tekton->>Tekton: git-clone → buildah build<br/>→ SBOM generation
    Tekton->>Registry: Push multi-arch image<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Push secret
    Tekton->>Tekton: Generate SBOM<br/>+ image index creation
